WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
How to plan your trip in Manta Transit.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:06.500
Step 1: Enter your starting point in the Origin field.

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Step 2: Enter your destination and press Search Route.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Step 3: Select the most convenient route from the list.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.500
Step 4: Confirm your trip and follow the live map.

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.000
Mobility for everyone. Your city in motion.
